# Adaptive Difficulty Click Game ğŸ¯

An intelligent clicking game that uses **machine learning** to dynamically adjust difficulty in real-time based on player performance. Built with Python, Pygame, and scikit-learn.

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)
![Pygame](https://img.shields.io/badge/pygame-2.0+-green.svg)
